903
00:40:36,960 --> 00:40:38,079
What if we don't?

904
00:40:38,239 --> 00:40:39,360
What will happen to him?

905
00:40:39,360 --> 00:40:40,920
If we don't intubate a nasogastric tube...

906
00:40:41,079 --> 00:40:43,880
