915
00:40:58,289 --> 00:41:00,360
Optimistically, it should be about six months.

916
00:41:01,079 --> 00:41:02,159
Okay, I got it.

917
00:41:03,440 --> 00:41:04,519
Mom.

918
00:41:05,000 --> 00:41:06,360
The tube needs to be inserted.

919
