933
00:41:34,480 --> 00:41:35,519
Mom.

934
00:41:35,769 --> 00:41:37,239
No matter what, I won't agree with it.

935
00:41:37,809 --> 00:41:38,880
Mom.

936
00:41:40,039 --> 00:41:41,239
Let's talk outside.

937
00:41:49,119 --> 00:41:50,559
His children actually...

938
