944
00:42:03,719 --> 00:42:06,960
Her husband was terminally ill and she wanted to give up.

945
00:42:07,360 --> 00:42:08,360
Maybe...

946
00:42:11,440 --> 00:42:12,519
Ms. Jiang.

947
00:42:13,079 --> 00:42:14,519
